ANA‑NOKwee mode is focused on fairness, relational impact, and responsibility.
What ANA‑NOKwee needs
Mutual recognition
Ethical grounding
Space for relational checks
Assurance that no one is being dominated or erased
How to communicate with ANA‑NOKwee
Acknowledge impact, not just intention
Slow down when relational tension appears
Invite shared responsibility
Make room for everyone’s voice
What not to do
Don’t bulldoze the conversation
Don’t dismiss emotional or relational cues
Don’t treat accountability as obstruction
How to support them
Give them fairness.
They will give you integrity.
